  "comment": "LCB128IP LED Bar IP65 12x 8W RGBA: The LCB128IP is a robust aluminium BAR specifically designed for outside usage. By using the latest LED technology the LCB128IP is able to create beautiful wash effects. The fixture is suitable for a wide range of applications from uplighting a large venue or building to lighting up a stage for live performances. The bar also sports a convection cooled cast aluminium housing with watertight internal gaskets and weatherproof power and DMX cable in/out leads. It comes with an infrared remote control.",
